    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty in person! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I have taken such incredible care of this car, and it\u2019s honestly in flawless, showroom-ready shape. It drives like a total dream and looks just as stunning as the day it was first bought. If you've been looking for a real gem that\u2019s been pampered its whole life, this is definitely the one for you! Drop me a message\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
