      "description": "Offered is a clinically maintained 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the 3.8L DFI flat-six mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. This example exhibits zero mechanical lash, with the PASM active dampers and factory-spec limited-slip differential performing to exacting tolerances. The chassis retains its original rigidity, and the atmospheric induction provides a linear torque curve free of hesitation. Meticulously preserved with a comprehensive service history, this vehicle presents in a showroom-fresh state, from its flawless undercarriage to the pristine engine bay. A turn-key acquisition for the discerning purist seeking peak analog performance.",
